### ❌ Test thiếu token
POST http://localhost:8080/favorites/toggle
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": 1
}

###

### ❌ Test thiếu roomId
POST http://localhost:8080/favorites/toggle
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### ❌ Test room không tồn tại
POST http://localhost:8080/favorites/toggle
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": 9999
}